 
<p>
*The ferocious heatwave that is gripping much of the US south and west
has highlighted an uncomfortable, ominous trend &mdash; people are continuing
to <a href="https://www.theguardian.com/us-news/2022/jul/20/us-fastest-growing-cities-risk-becoming-unlivable-climate-crisis">flock to the cities that risk becoming unlivable due to the climate
crisis</a>.*

 